	<!-- 
		Page Location Groups ::: uhendba : 0229
		groups of coordinates used to arrange islands on page
		- @size - max islands per page (referenced by defaults by the number of islands in a partition)
		- @name - OPTIONAL: named group for custom location groups (referenced in partitions)
		- @scale - OPTIONAL: custom scale for islands
	-->
