	<!-- 
		::: Island Partitions ::: uhendba : 0229
		partitions added to separate islands into their own "groups" e.g. "Starter Islands", "Easy Islands" etc.
		- islands within partitions will be shown in their own "page(s)"
		- @name - partitions with name attribute assigned will have a banner with the name appear below the islands
		- @group - OPTIONAL: @name of custom location group to use 
	-->
